casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Lance William RUIMVELD, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 158406
COA: 344040 Supreme Court of Michigan. February 4, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the July 17, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
